<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 04:09:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>据报道，25 名加沙人在拉法罢工中丧生；以色列国防军：首次探测未表明那里遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-live/25-gazans-reported-dead-in-rafah-strike-idf-first-probe-does-not-indicate-strike-there/00000190-3dea-d8cb-a19d-7debec640005</link><description>叙利亚报道：不明身份飞机袭击叙利亚和伊拉克边境附近地区 ■ 卡塔尔表示，尽管加沙停火谈判取得了一些进展，但差距仍然存在 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部称，以色列国防军袭击拉法流离失所者的帐篷，造成 25 人死亡、50 人受伤 ■ 医院加沙城主任：以色列多处袭击造成约 30 人死亡 ■ 亚美尼亚宣布承认巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 03:20:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-live/25-gazans-reported-dead-in-rafah-strike-idf-first-probe-does-not-indicate-strike-there/00000190-3dea-d8cb-a19d-7debec640005</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡前雇员因欺凌、侵犯权利而获得 24 万美元赔偿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/former-netanyahu-employees-to-receive-240-000-for-bullying-rights-violations/00000190-3b89-da42-a1ba-7feb2c6e0000</link><description>两名维修工感觉自己像“现代奴隶”，其中一名经常违反程序被派往该家庭的私人住宅清洁游泳池。一名在该住所工作的厨师声称没有获得加班费</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 03:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/former-netanyahu-employees-to-receive-240-000-for-bullying-rights-violations/00000190-3b89-da42-a1ba-7feb2c6e0000</guid></item><item><title>去年，我决定放弃我的犹太身份。事情没有按计划进行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/last-year-i-decided-to-turn-my-back-on-my-jewish-identity-it-didnt-go-as-planned/00000190-3ccf-da42-a1ba-7fefec8a0000</link><description>我对内塔尼亚胡-本-格维尔政府成立的最初反应是冷落我的犹太教，但我的尝试失败了——就像许多试图逃避民族身份但失败的人一样</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 22:23:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/last-year-i-decided-to-turn-my-back-on-my-jewish-identity-it-didnt-go-as-planned/00000190-3ccf-da42-a1ba-7fefec8a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列微小的切尔克斯社区在炮火中保持其烹饪传统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-06-22/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-tiny-circassian-community-maintains-its-culinary-traditions-under-fire/00000190-3c99-d91c-abba-ff9980cf0000</link><description>在以色列北部的卡夫卡马，餐馆提供以传统切尔克斯奶酪为基础的美味佳肴。在它的姊妹村雷哈尼亚 (Rehaniya)，美食旅游业被战争摧毁，当地企业正在艰难生存</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 21:58:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-06-22/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-tiny-circassian-community-maintains-its-culinary-traditions-under-fire/00000190-3c99-d91c-abba-ff9980cf0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日：两次比较——以及一个已实现的预测</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/october-7-two-comparisons-and-a-forecast-that-was-realized/00000190-3c45-d8cb-a19d-7d47bcde0000</link><description>与每一个历史事件一样，八个多月前的哈马斯大屠杀是独一无二的，但它可以分为不同的层次，可以与类似事件进行比较，从而加深我们对它的理解</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 20:58:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/october-7-two-comparisons-and-a-forecast-that-was-realized/00000190-3c45-d8cb-a19d-7d47bcde0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-巴勒斯坦和平可能与我们想象的完全不同</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israeli-palestinian-peace-may-look-entirely-different-from-how-we-imagine-it/00000190-3c3a-d16c-a7b0-7ebf4ae40000</link><description>各国人民之间的和平不一定是爱情故事，也可以建立在利益联盟的基础上。由于“和平变革”的进程，有些地方已经发挥了作用</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:51:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israeli-palestinian-peace-may-look-entirely-different-from-how-we-imagine-it/00000190-3c3a-d16c-a7b0-7ebf4ae40000</guid></item><item><title>作为美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 的战地记者，阿尔瓦·达蒙 (Arwa Damon) 认为她已经看到了一切。然后她去了加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/as-a-cnn-war-reporter-arwa-damon-thought-she-had-seen-everything-then-she-went-to-gaza/00000190-3bdd-d768-adf8-3fff8a400000</link><description>叙利亚内战期间，她通过下水道进入霍姆斯，后来亲眼目睹了伊斯兰国在摩苏尔制造的恐怖。作为美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 的高级记者，阿尔瓦·达蒙 (Arwa Damon) 报道了中东最严重的战区。但没有一个地方比加沙更可怕，她作为人道主义组织负责人访问了加沙：“我看到了人类灵魂的死亡”</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/as-a-cnn-war-reporter-arwa-damon-thought-she-had-seen-everything-then-she-went-to-gaza/00000190-3bdd-d768-adf8-3fff8a400000</guid></item><item><title>纽约时报：以色列的斯莫特里奇记录了加强对约旦河西岸控制的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/nyt-israels-smotrich-recorded-describing-plan-to-increase-control-over-west-bank/00000190-3c0d-d768-adf8-3cbf01e40000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇讨论的计划将赋予国防部内为他工作的文职人员而不是军队在被占领土上更多的权力，该计划已在过去 18 个月内逐步实施</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:14:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/nyt-israels-smotrich-recorded-describing-plan-to-increase-control-over-west-bank/00000190-3c0d-d768-adf8-3cbf01e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方以暴力、错误逮捕和监视镇压抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-police-crack-down-on-protesters-with-violence-false-arrests-and-surveillance/00000190-3a6a-dea6-add5-faea16460000</link><description>六月标志着警察和示威者之间关系的转折点，民意调查显示，许多以色列人害怕参加因暴力事件不断升级而举行的抗议活动</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 17:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-police-crack-down-on-protesters-with-violence-false-arrests-and-surveillance/00000190-3a6a-dea6-add5-faea16460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 259 天：以色列军队加大对加沙地带的攻击力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-259-israeli-army-steps-up-attacks-across-the-gaza-strip/00000190-3bba-d49b-a1bd-7bfbdb960000</link><description>以色列国防军袭击加沙全境 ■ 人质之母：不会让内塔尼亚胡“背着人质玩小政治” ■ 美国国务院：就内塔尼亚胡视频反复讨论不会“有成效” ■ 亚美尼亚承认巴勒斯坦国■ 战争进入 259 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 17:11:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-259-israeli-army-steps-up-attacks-across-the-gaza-strip/00000190-3bba-d49b-a1bd-7bfbdb960000</guid></item><item><title>无人机没有铁穹：以色列国防军寻求解决真主党日益严重的威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/no-iron-dome-for-drones-idf-seeks-answers-to-growing-hezbollah-threat/00000190-3b38-d49b-a1bd-7b79f46b0000</link><description>真主党成功地挑战了以色列的防空系统，部分原因在于它在叙利亚内战中获得的经验。当以色列军队寻求新的防御方法时，武装直升机已被证明出奇的有效</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 17:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/no-iron-dome-for-drones-idf-seeks-answers-to-growing-hezbollah-threat/00000190-3b38-d49b-a1bd-7b79f46b0000</guid></item><item><title>21 岁巴勒斯坦人被控四月在约旦河西岸谋杀以色列青少年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/21-year-old-palestinian-charged-with-murder-of-israeli-teen-in-west-bank-in-april/00000190-3a98-da42-a1ba-7ffa08ad0000</link><description>起诉书称，艾哈迈德·达瓦布沙一年前对伊斯兰国产生了兴趣，并认为每个非穆斯林都是异教徒。军法署署长表示，在杀害 14 岁犹太牧羊人本雅明·阿希米尔后，达瓦布沙寻找更多受害者</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 16:08:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/21-year-old-palestinian-charged-with-murder-of-israeli-teen-in-west-bank-in-april/00000190-3a98-da42-a1ba-7ffa08ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以军加速拉法突击 坦克向北和西推进</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-accelerates-rafah-assaults-tanks-advancing-northward-and-westward/00000190-3ac5-d768-adf8-3ef74df50000</link><description>加沙地带南部城市的居民报告说，过去两天，以色列国防军从海上和空中发动袭击时，不断发生爆炸和枪击事件。拉法市长：由于轰炸，“人们正在帐篷里死去”</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:58:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-accelerates-rafah-assaults-tanks-advancing-northward-and-westward/00000190-3ac5-d768-adf8-3ef74df50000</guid></item><item><title>亚美尼亚宣布承认巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/armenia-announces-recognition-of-palestinian-state/00000190-39e3-d768-adf8-3df3ea000000</link><description>该国外交部称，加沙地带持续的战争和严峻的人道主义局势是其做出这一决定的原因。以色列召见亚美尼亚大使予以谴责</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 12:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/armenia-announces-recognition-of-palestinian-state/00000190-39e3-d768-adf8-3df3ea000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将为非洲寻求庇护者提供健康保险，但大多数人不符合资格</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-offer-health-insurance-to-african-asylum-seekers-but-most-wont-be-eligible/00000190-3a4a-d49b-a1bd-7b7bf5a70000</link><description>财政部和卫生部签署了新规定，允许寻求庇护者购买健康保险，但仅限未成年人和 60 岁以上的人。人权组织表示，患有严重或慢性疾病的人以及残疾人没有资格获得保险，并受到批评成本高</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 11:45:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-offer-health-insurance-to-african-asylum-seekers-but-most-wont-be-eligible/00000190-3a4a-d49b-a1bd-7b7bf5a70000</guid></item><item><title>塞西和埃尔多安已经认识到，你无法消除思想。内塔尼亚胡还没有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/al-sissi-and-erdogan-already-learned-that-you-cant-eradicate-ideas-netanyahu-hasnt/00000190-399a-d8cb-a19d-79dbf8ee0000</link><description>如果埃及总统对穆斯林兄弟会的全面战争以及土耳其总统埃尔多安针对居伦运动长达十年的斗争是可以参考的，那么哈马斯很可能在内塔尼亚胡的“全面胜利”中幸存下来。</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 10:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/al-sissi-and-erdogan-already-learned-that-you-cant-eradicate-ideas-netanyahu-hasnt/00000190-399a-d8cb-a19d-79dbf8ee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名两名在加沙战斗中丧生的预备役军人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-two-reservists-killed-in-gaza-fighting/00000190-3936-d91c-abba-ff36bad30000</link><description>来自加诺·哈达尔（Ganot Hadar）的 25 岁中士奥马尔·斯马德加（Omer Smadga）和来自特拉维夫的 27 岁中士萨迪亚·雅科夫·德里（Saadia Yaakov Dery）在此次事件中丧生，三名预备役军人身受重伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 06:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-two-reservists-killed-in-gaza-fighting/00000190-3936-d91c-abba-ff36bad30000</guid></item><item><title>从特朗普到本格维尔，愤世嫉俗的破坏者内塔尼亚胡都站在了错误的一边</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/from-trump-to-ben-gvir-netanyahu-the-cynical-saboteur-picks-all-the-wrong-sides/00000190-371f-d6fa-abb4-77bfc96c0000</link><description>干涉美国总统选举后，内塔尼亚胡将自己归为历史错误一边的领导人。 本-格维尔和总理正在进行类似的竞选活动，其中至少有一个让我们想起了我们宁愿做的事情忘记了 ■ 谁嫉妒戈特利夫和萨达的 15 分钟成名？</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:08:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/from-trump-to-ben-gvir-netanyahu-the-cynical-saboteur-picks-all-the-wrong-sides/00000190-371f-d6fa-abb4-77bfc96c0000</guid></item><item><title>无休止的战争，而不是“全面胜利”：以色列国防军想要离开加沙，但内塔尼亚胡有其他想法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/endless-war-not-total-victory-idf-wants-to-leave-gaza-but-netanyahu-has-other-ideas/00000190-368a-d8bc-abf7-b7ba30d00000</link><description>当以色列军队和公众准备结束加沙的战斗，将注意力集中在北部日益激烈的战争时，内塔尼亚胡陷入了他一贯偏执的政治网络中，其中包括琐碎的口号和恶意的指责游戏，他接受了枪击在以色列国防军、抗议者、拜登和所有阻碍他的人</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/endless-war-not-total-victory-idf-wants-to-leave-gaza-but-netanyahu-has-other-ideas/00000190-368a-d8bc-abf7-b7ba30d00000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，25 名加沙人在拉法罢工中丧生；以色列国防军：首次探测未表明那里遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-live/blinken-urges-israeli-officials-to-avoid-further-escalation-with-hezbollah/00000190-3888-d49b-a1bd-7bf986180000</link><description>卡塔尔表示，尽管加沙停火谈判取得了一些进展，但差距仍然存在。 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部表示，以色列国防军袭击拉法流离失所者的帐篷，造成 25 人死亡、50 人受伤。 ■ 加沙市医院院长：以色列袭击数个城市，造成约 30 人死亡地点 ■ 亚美尼亚宣布承认巴勒斯坦国 ■ 以色列国防军证实击毙了哈马斯无人机操作员；伊斯兰圣战发射场被摧毁 ■ 美国称自加沙临时码头重新锚定以来已卸载 656 吨援助物资</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 02:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-live/blinken-urges-israeli-officials-to-avoid-further-escalation-with-hezbollah/00000190-3888-d49b-a1bd-7bf986180000</guid></item></channel></rss>